Text: Re Bridal ShowerDana Yes I am still giving Edith her bridal shower on this upcoming weekend And I do believe your name was included in the invitations that were sent out which was this past Monday So you should be receiving directions as well as the invitation sometime this week Thanks for inquiring and hope to have you join us on Saturdaytalk soon Kathy Kathy D Lacy REP Dana n roncom To om PM cc Subject Re Bridal Shower Hi Kathy Im Dana Davis A member of Veterans Memorial are you still sending informationdirections regarding Ediths bridal shower on Dec nd Forwarded by Dana DavisHOUECT on PM on AM To cc Subject Re Bridal Shower Im resending this email because it appears that I am having problems forwarding to my sisters email address The address is If you care to respond please remember to copy me as well and Im sure one of us will get the information For those of you who did receive this email the first time please scroll down Thank you Edith
